documents.description: Will you be able to accomplish all of the objectives in this super sweet match 3 puzzle game? Quickly link together the candy as fast as you can based on the challenges listed at the top of the board. You’ll have to play fast if you want to beat the clock!
documents.title: Sweet Candy

documents.description: You can dress up your snake as Santa Claus, a vampire, or even a chicken in this weird and wacky multiplayer action game. Find out if you can turn your snake into the raddest reptile in this battle arena. Guide it as it gobbles up tons of power pellets and attempts to avoid the other slithering combatants.
documents.title: Worms.io

documents.description:
The world famous feline is ready to take you on a magical journey in Hello Kitty Mahjong. It’s her very own online version of the classic puzzle game! 

 

There’s two dozen boards in this Mahjong game that will really test your skills. Some of them are pretty tough! How fast will you be able to connect all of the tiles? Step through the doors that feature an adorable picture of Hello Kitty where they’re all waiting for you. 

 

Can you connect tiles that feature yummy apples, cute bows, and bottles of delicious milk? Oh, and there’s a few that also have Hello Kitty on them, too! You won’t have much time during each fun and exciting level. Match up the tiles as fast as you can! 

 

Hello Kitty Mahjong is just one of our many puzzle games. You can also play Butterfly Kyodai Classic and MahJongCon.

 

 

Game Controls

 

LEFT CLICK on the Mahjong tiles to match them.
documents.title: Hello Kitty Mahjong

documents.description: Summertime is here! Can you help these fashionable princesses design the best outfits and accessories they can for the season? They want to look totally awesome in this online dress-up game.
documents.title: Princesses: Colors of Summer

documents.description: Belt bags are cool, and they really make it easy to carry around your stuff while you’re at a festival, a concert, or another awesome event. Can you help these stylish princesses choose some that will look great with their latest outfits? They could really use your advice in this dress-up and design game.
documents.title: Princesses: Belt Bag Fashion

documents.description: Will you become a master on the court in this challenging sports game? See if you can get the basketball through the hoop in each level while you try to collect three stars. You’ll be facing down some tough competition, though. These other players have awesome skills!
documents.title: Basketball Master 2

documents.description: How will all of this colorful sand get into the dump truck? That’s for you to figure out in this addictive puzzle game! Dig caves through the ground that will get the sand to the truck. You’ll need to carefully create the cave’s path while you try to get around various obstacles.
documents.title: Sand Balls

documents.description: The sun is shining, the birds are singing, and these three princesses are getting ready for a chill afternoon at their favorite swimming pool. Which swimsuits should they wear, though? Can you help them get ready for some maximum relaxation in this dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Princesses: Chilling at the Pool

documents.description: There’s lots of different types of slushies that you can make in this online simulation game. You can prepare one of these delicious and icy drinks with kiwis, mangoes, blueberries, and so much more. There’s also several virtual ice trays you can try out that will create cubes shaped like hearts, diamonds, and other awesome stuff.
documents.title: Ice Slushy Maker

documents.description: One or two players can fight their way through this strategic medieval action and tower defense game. Team up with a group of fearless knights while they try to defend their kingdom from some really annoying trolls and other monsters. They can battle them with arrows, swords, and really cool magic spells. They’ll be relying on you to build towers and provide them with awesome upgrades, though.
documents.title: Vera Towers

documents.description: A new school year is about to begin at this enchanted academy. Join this student and her friend the genie while they work on some awesome magical spells. Each one will help her create an awesome new classmate!
documents.title: Spell Factory: Back to School

documents.description: Tons of fun is waiting for you in this delightful and super cute puzzle game. You can put together funny pictures of a penguin on a ski slope, a turtle hanging out at a playground, and even a crocodile working on her latest sewing project. How fast can you put together each jigsaw puzzle?
documents.title: Kids Jigsaw Puzzles: Zoo Fun

documents.description: How many tanks will you blow to smithereens in this multiplayer action game? Fight alongside the Blue Team or join the Red Team for a series of super awesome battles. You’ll only have a certain amount of time during each one, so blast as many of your opponents to bits as possible. You can even upgrade your tank with cool weapons and armor between battles.
documents.title: Tank Off

documents.description: Oh no! These adorable animals are all trapped in cages! Can you break them free in this cute and challenging puzzle game? Form a connection between the keys and the cages by placing the shapes in the correct spots. There’s also cool boosters you can use that will help the animals escape.
documents.title: Blocks Puzzle Zoo

documents.description: Annie and Eliza are getting ready to take their favorite social media app by storm! Help them impress their followers with lots of awesome outfits and some really cool hairstyles in this dress-up and design game. Will you be able to create the perfect styles for each one of their daily challenges?
documents.title: Annie and Eliza's: Social Media Adventure

documents.description: Max, Sonya, and their friends are members of an elite squad of commandos. Team up with them for a series of exciting missions in this online action game. They’ll be using awesome equipment like bounce guns and the mysterious Weapon X to take down their targets. You can also upgrade their abilities between missions.
documents.title: Alpha Guns

documents.description: This garden is in pretty sad shape! Fortunately, these two princesses are coming to the rescue! Can you lend them a hand in this online design and gardening simulation game? They’re about to completely restore it with lots of awesome plants, flowers, and other features!
documents.title: Princesses: Garden Rescue

documents.description: How long will you last in this super intense action game? There’s tons of weird objects that are trying to destroy your tank. Blast them as fast as you can. Some of them are really powerful and will require you to shoot them several times.
documents.title: Ball Blast

documents.description: These three princesses just received an invitation to an elegant ball in the magical kingdom of Fairyland. They’ll need the right outfits for the occasion, needless to say! Can you help them create the perfect gowns before they begin their magical journey in this online dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Princesses Visiting Fairyland

documents.description: Cities and forests can be dangerous places when you’re a raccoon. Can you help this one look for all the food it needs in this 3D simulation game? It’ll need to track down some tasty grub while it avoids pesky humans and other annoying hazards.
documents.title: Raccoon Adventure: City Simulator 3D

documents.description: How fast can you merge together all of these cute kitties? It’s a unique challenge that’s waiting for you in this purr-fect version of the popular puzzle game 2048. Do your best to keep making room for all of these cats before they fill up the entire board.
documents.title: Cat Story 2048

documents.description: You might actually go ballistic while you play this challenging puzzle game! Take a quick look at the numbers on all of the blocks that are falling down the screen. You’ll need to hit them each exactly that number of times to make them go away. Can you stop them from reaching the bottom?
documents.title: Ballistic

documents.description: This brave warrior really puts the grr in girl! She’s determined to beat the robot in each one of their thrilling competitions. Help her use walls, reactors, and lasers to blast the robot’s equipment to bits! Can you and her defeat her futuristic foe in this challenging puzzle game?
documents.title: Lazer Grrl

documents.description: A new school year has just begun! Fill this locker full of all sorts of useful essentials like rulers and notebooks. You can also decorate cool stuff like pencil holders and backpacks in this online design game.
documents.title: Back to School: Locker Essentials

documents.description: Tomorrow is this busy princess’ wedding day, and she isn’t quite ready for it. Can you help her make sure that everything will be totally perfect in this bridal dress-up game? She still needs to do her nails, choose her makeup, and put the finishing touches on her gown.
documents.title: Princess: The Day Before My Wedding

documents.description: These space aliens just messed with the wrong commando! They kidnapped Fluffy, his pet squid, and now he’s determined to rescue him. Join the commando as he fights back in this interstellar action game. With your help, and tons of awesome weapons and upgrades, he should be able to find Fluffy in no time.
documents.title: Mad Day: Special

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep playing this exciting basketball game? Try to get the ball through the hoop in each pulse-pounding level. You won’t have much time to make each shot, so you’ll have to move fast!
documents.title: Basketball Smash

documents.description: These two princesses want to become popular influencers. You can help them get started with some quick makeovers in this online dress-up and design game. Which types of makeup should they try out? What awesome outfits should they share with all of their new followers? It’s almost time for them to decide!
documents.title: Princess Influencer: Summer Tale

documents.description: Can you squeeze all of these wooden puzzle pieces into the slots on the board? Try to make space for them in this challenging puzzle game. Will you earn a high-score?
documents.title: Block Wood Puzzle

documents.description: In very remote regions, it can be tough to transport train carriages. That’s why you’ll get to use a variety of tractors in this online simulation game. See if you can move the carriages and other train components along railways located on the slopes of rugged mountains. Will you be able to get them all to the correct stations?
documents.title: Tractor Towing Train

documents.description: Sometimes it’s tough to be a Tooth Fairy. The hours are long, you’ve got to work at night, and there’s no time for fashion! Can you help this one choose an outfit and some awesome makeup for tonight in this magical dress-up game? She overslept, she’s running late, and she has no idea what to wear!
documents.title: Tooth Fairy Lifestyle

documents.description: Even famous puppies love fashion! Can you help their owners create some dashing outfits for these adorable doggies? You’ll need to bathe and groom them first in this cool and totally cute simulation, dress-up, and design game.
documents.title: Celebrity Puppies

documents.description: How fast can you match up all of this delicious candy? Find out once you take control of the marvelous machine in this bubble shooter game. Carefully shoot each piece of candy toward at least two others of the same kind. That will make them disappear. You can even switch between two different types of candy while you plan each shot.
documents.title: Sweet Candy Mania

documents.description: This ball is determined to reach the bottom of each one of these towers. Help it blast through all of the floors as it makes its way toward the ground in this intense action game. It’ll need to avoid areas of a certain color, though! If it hits those, it’ll go splat!
documents.title: Tower Ball 3D

documents.description: These pesky pinatas won’t know what hit them in this totally insane and incredibly addictive action game! You can hit them with everything from chainsaws to Molotov cocktails. Pummel them into oblivion while you gather coins to buy even cooler weapons, but watch out. If you run out of ammo or fuel, they’ll laugh at you before they make their escape!
documents.title: Pinata Master Online

documents.description: This girl just had her heart broken by her boyfriend. Can you help her get over their break-up in this online makeover and design game? She’s going to focus on a makeover that will give her a whole new style. You can choose some fresh makeup for her along with lots of awesome outfits and accessories.
documents.title: Sisters: Break-Up Plan

documents.description: Will you be able to keep the black dot moving in this intense action game? Find out if you can lead it to all of the goals in each thrilling level. A rising tide of evil goo is determined to destroy it!
documents.title: Outjump

documents.description: Will you be able to reassemble all of these adorable pictures of cats? There’s a dozen of them that you can work on in this online jigsaw puzzle game.
documents.title: Jigsaw Puzzle: Cartoon Cats

documents.description: You can create and customize entire kingdoms in this world-building simulation game. Go exploring through lush meadows and past picturesque ponds after you adjust them by moving around the various blocks.
documents.title: Mine Clone 4

documents.description: These princesses are supposedly friends, but they never seem to get along. Now they’re both trying to date the same boy at their school! Which one of these frenemies will win his heart in this wild and romantic dress-up game? Choose the perfect music mix for them while they both try to create outfits that will really attract his attention.
documents.title: Princess: Best Frenemy

documents.description: What colors will pop up when these princesses spin the Fashion Wheel? You can find out in this cool dress-up and design game. They’ll need to create outfits that feature the colors. Can you help them make some styles that really shine?
documents.title: Princesses: Colors Roulette

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep moving through this mysterious laboratory? Use your powerful spheres to smash everything you can in this 3D action game. You’ll need to keep up with the meter while you destroy as many triangles and boxes as you can.
documents.title: Smash Hit

documents.description: Play against a friend or challenge the computer in this version of the classic tabletop game. Will you be able to get four of your discs to line up before they do?
documents.title: 4 in a Row Mania

documents.description: You can create several different works of art featuring super cute animals in this online design game. It’ll let you make awesome elephants, penguins, cats, and much more! All you need to do is put the correct color in each one of the numbered squares.
documents.title: Color by Number: Animals

documents.description: This girl’s BFF is about to get married, and they’re getting stuff ready for her big day. Can you help them make sure everything will be totally perfect in this dress-up and design game? They still need to choose their dresses, get manicures, and put up lots of gorgeous decorations.
documents.title: My BFF's Wedding

documents.description: There’s some very busy weeks coming up at this popular lunch spot. Will you be able to make tons of delicious club sandwiches for all of its customers? You’ll have to stay focused and work fast in this online business simulation game. Make sure you use all the right ingredients and don’t forget the soda if someone orders a beverage with their meal.
documents.title: Club Sandwich

documents.description: This superhero has a super sore throat! She’s waiting for you to give her a quick exam at a clinic in her hometown of Paris. Can you figure out what’s causing the problem in this medical simulation game? She wants to get back to fighting various super-villains in the French capital, and she really doesn’t have time for this!
documents.title: Dotted Girl: Throat Doctor

documents.description: Join a team and dive into a thrilling competition in this edition of Kogama, the popular world-building simulation game. Your goal is to capture your opponents’ flag while using a few cool parkour maneuvers to avoid a series of deadly traps. Will you be able to grab their flag before they make it to yours?
documents.title: Kogama: 4 Players Parkour

documents.description: It’s another busy day in the life of this hardworking miner. He’s got trees to chop down, mines to dig, and valuable minerals to collect. He’ll even need to repair his tools every once in a while. Can you help him achieve all of his daily goals in this retro online game?
documents.title: Miner Dash

documents.description: Ollie was just trying to enjoy a nap when his owner decided it was time for him to go to school. Can you help the very cute bunny prepare for what’s sure to be a long day in this hilarious online game? You’ll need to feed him carrots, get him dressed, make sure all of his school supplies are in his backpack, and more!
documents.title: Ollie Goes to School

documents.description: All of these patients are dealing with some very odd problems involving their ears. Can you figure out what’s causing all the trouble in this hilarious medical simulation game? There’s no telling what you’ll discover once you get them into the examination room in this clinic. They might need surgery!
documents.title: Funny Ear Surgery

documents.description: You can climb into the cockpit of a Boeing passenger jet in this 3D flight simulator game. Transport your passengers safely to their destinations while you fly in and out of various international airports. There’s also a smaller private plane that you can try out as well.
documents.title: Boeing Flight Simulator

documents.description: Prove that you’ve got a green thumb in this fun io game. You’ll need to raise crops faster than your opponents. You can grow yummy vegetables like carrots, but you’ll need to give them fertilizer and make sure that they’re well watered. How many will you wind up with once it’s time for the harvest?
documents.title: Farmerz.io

documents.description: These four BFFs are not having a good time at their friend’s wedding. She’s turning into a complete bridezilla! Now they have to change their outfits to prevent her from completely losing her cool. Can you help them quickly put together some new ones in this outrageous and outrageously fun dress-up game?
documents.title: BFFs: Turning into Bridezilla

documents.description: How long will you be able to protect all of this cursed treasure? There’s villagers, knights, and powerful monsters who are all determined to steal it from you in this epic tower defense game. Build enchanted temples, crypts, and dens to defeat them while you earn awesome upgrades that will help you keep fighting during your thrilling adventure.
documents.title: Cursed Treasure

documents.description: You can play against a few friendly automated opponents in this awesome and very cute version of the classic board game. There’s also an online mode that will let you challenge other players from all around the world. Can you get each one of your tokens to the home area before they do?
documents.title: Ludo With Friends

documents.description: Style wish lists are a great way to keep track of new and cool looks that you want to try out. That’s why these three princesses have just updated theirs with lots of awesome ideas. Can you help them create some really fantastic outfits in this dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Princesses: Style Wish List

documents.description: You’ll need to stay fast on your feet if you want to survive for longer than a few seconds in this action-packed and very retro io game. Try to find a weapon like a powerful shotgun as quickly as you can along with lots of cool boosters and useful health packs. Your enemies will show you no mercy, so don’t go easy on them!
documents.title: Helmet Royale.io

documents.description: Autumn is a great time of the year for a school camping trip. Can you help these stylish students decide what to take with them in this dress-up and design game? They’ll need to choose some comfy and warm outfits along with plenty of useful gear. Help them choose the right clothes, tents, snacks, and other stuff they should pack.
documents.title: Camping School Trip

documents.description: How many bricks can you remove from this castle before it collapses? Spin the platform it’s sitting on while you carefully plan your every move in this 3D puzzle game. Find out how many points you can earn before the castle crumbles!
documents.title: Castle Puzzle

documents.description: It’s another busy day in Watts’ laboratory. He’s teaming up with his assistant Monroe to build a super awesome robot panther. They’ll have to work fast in this futuristic action game. The city might be under attack at any second! They’re definitely going to need your help to complete the panther before their enemies show up.
documents.title: Robot Police Iron Panther

documents.description: It’s a very busy afternoon in this ER! Will you be able to quickly treat each one of these seven patients? They all have unusual injuries in this weird and wacky medical simulation game. There’s even a mailman who was bit by a dog. Well, he’s actually still being bitten by the dog. You’ll need to remove the horrendous hound once you get him into the operating room!
documents.title: Emergency Surgery

documents.description: You can try out many different vehicles in this 3D driving game. Several of them are the type of cars you might find in an off-road derby while others are better suited for combat! Which one will you try to avoid crashing first?
documents.title: Derby Crash 2

documents.description: Ellie was in a serious accident recently. She’s currently at home recovering from her injuries, and it could be a while before she’s able to return to work. Can you help her get better in this online medical simulation game?
documents.title: Ellie: Home Recovery

documents.description: This stickman can swing through the air thanks to his handy-dandy web shooters. He’ll need you to keep him from crashing though in this exciting action game. Help him swing along the elevated posts while he tries to reach the finish line in each challenging level.
documents.title: Stickman Swing

documents.description: These girls are putting their design skills to work on a cute project in this online game. They’re going to be creating some comfy outfits before they start designing a few really cosy blankets. Can you help them out with some quick advice to make sure their project is totally awesome?
documents.title: My Cosy Blanket Design

documents.description: Will you be able to get this mysterious box through each one of these tricky levels? Find out if you can move it to the portals in this 3D puzzle game. It’s tougher than it might seem at first glance!
documents.title: Portal Box

documents.description: This clever chef has tons of cakes piling up in his kitchen. Can you help him get rid of them in this bubble shooter game? Rather than throwing them in the trash, he’s decided to destroy the cakes with a super awesome cannon!
documents.title: Happy Chef: Bubble Shooter

documents.description: An epic series of battles is already underway in this futuristic multiplayer shooter game. Team up with a robot before you go in search of your enemies. Will you be able to send them to the scrap heap? Choose a bot and a gun before you challenge other gamers from all over the world. Just don’t forget to use the portals if you really find yourself in a jam!
documents.title: Robofight.io

documents.description: Who will become queen within the enchanted land in this online puzzle and dress-up game? Team up with a group of magical dolls while they try to take their kingdom back from their really wicked rivals. During their quest, they’ll need your help while they complete puzzles and create some awesome outfits along the way!
documents.title: Road to Royalty: Battle of Dolls

documents.description: Annie is experimenting with two awesome styles in this online dress-up and design game. Can you help her create the perfect vintage outfit before she works on a more modern look? Once she’s done, she’s going to try combining items from both outfits to create a super stylish remix!
documents.title: Annie's Vintage Modern Remix

documents.description: Alu, the guardian of this ancient temple, is furious! Someone stole his socks, and now he’s blaming you! Will you be able to appease him by destroying all of the stone soldiers in this weird and wild match 3 puzzle game? Maybe that will calm him down.
documents.title: Alu's Revenge 2

documents.description: These cars got canned a few days ago. Naturally, they were pretty upset. They kinda started a riot, and now they’re in prison. Can you help them escape in this weird and wild racing game? They’ll need to avoid the police and collect powerful boosters while they try to make it to Freedom Island where they’ll be able to live in peace.
documents.title: Car Eats Car: Evil Cars

documents.description: An army of mysterious monsters made out of paint are trying to invade the castle in this weird and wild tower defense game. Use your cash and resources wisely while you attempt to defeat them. You’ll need to design your own crazy creatures before you lead them into battle.
documents.title: Elf Tower Defense

documents.description: It’s almost time for these three girls to go on a vacation that will take them all around the world. They’re going to need plenty of awesome outfits and accessories for their exciting trip. Can you help them decide which ones to pack in this globe-trotting dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Girls Traveling Around the World

documents.description: She may live on a tropical island, but this princess has never been on a cruise before. Can you help her get ready in this dress-up and travel simulation game? She’ll need to pack some awesome outfits, makeup, and accessories.
documents.title: Island Princess: First Time Cruise

documents.description: How much do you remember about the geography of Europe? Test your knowledge of the continent and its borders with this challenging educational game. Will you be able to place each country in its correct location? You’ll need to figure out where to place France, Estonia, and many more nations!
documents.title: Scatty Maps: Europe

documents.description: Is this a brawl or a game of basketball? There’s only one way to find out! Blast your way past your opponents or knock them right out of town in this epic basketball and io game. Will your team be the first one to make it to one of the hoops on this urban court? Dunk your way to glory while you show the other team who’s boss.
documents.title: Basketball.io

documents.description: This young girl loves books, especially bedtime stories. Her mom is going to read her a few in this magical dress-up game. You can join her on an enchanting journey while she imagines participating in the stories herself. What types of awesome outfits would she wear before embarking on all sorts of amazing adventures? You can help her decide!
documents.title: Adventure Bedtime Stories

documents.description: How quickly can you make all of these tennis balls fall into the slots? Carefully twist and turn the maze in each challenging level that’s waiting for you in this puzzle game.
documents.title: Wobble 3D

documents.description: Annie is feeling very moody today. Maybe you can cheer her up in this online game? She could be grumpy, happy, or eager to work on a creative project, so you’ll need to be ready. You can make yummy snacks for her, join her while she designs outfits, or help her use her imagination while she participates in some super fun activities.
documents.title: Annie: Mood Swings

documents.description: How long will it take you to match up each one of the pieces of candy in this spinning wheel? Put them all into groups of three or more in this super sweet bubble shooter game. Play as fast as you can in order to earn a bonus worth lots of points.
documents.title: Bubble Shooter: Candy Wheel

documents.description: No one ever said that being a bus driver was easy! Will you be able to get your passengers to their destinations in this 3D driving simulation game? There’s a variety of buses you can drive, and your routes will lead you down some tricky roads filled with twists and turns. You can also improve your virtual driving skills in the timed mode or just go for a spin in the one that will let you simply roam around.
documents.title: Uphill Bus Simulator

documents.description: Mr. Pong loves to bounce around. However, like most disembodied heads, he can’t stand getting stabbed by spikes! How long will you be able to keep him moving in this super silly action game? Mr. Pong can’t stop jumping, and he doesn’t want to ruffle even a single hair on his marvelous mustache!
documents.title: Mr. Pong

documents.description: These princesses are hoping to enjoy some memorable moments during their vacation in Hawaii. Can you help them get ready in this dress-up and design game? You can create some awesome outfits they’ll be able to take with them. They’d like to wear a few colorful swimsuits and awesome summer dresses while they’re exploring the islands.
documents.title: Princess: Hawaiian Memories

documents.description: You can get your daily Sudoku fix in this online version of the classic mathematical puzzle game. Will you be able to beat its daily challenges? There’s different modes that will help everyone from beginners to expert players improve their Sudoku skills.
documents.title: Daily Sudoku 2

documents.description: Eliza is determined to have a fantastic wedding, but she’s going to need tons of help! She would like to hire you as her wedding planner in this online simulation and design game. Can you make sure that everything will be perfect for her big day? You’ll need to choose her gown, pick out her makeup, create her invitations, and much more.
documents.title: Eliza's Wedding Planner

documents.description: Look out! There’s tons of traffic on all of the very busy roadways in this exciting driving game. Will you be able to get your car across the finish line in each challenging level? You’ll need to merge into traffic, dodge buses, and get across freeways with four lanes. It won’t be easy!
documents.title: Traffic Run!

documents.description: You can explore the vast expanses of Russia in this majestic simulation game. Take control of vintage and modern locomotives while you transport both passengers and cargo. Will you be able to reach all of the checkpoints before time runs out?
documents.title: Russian Train Simulator

documents.description: There’s a huge concert tonight, and these fashionable girls are going to a rooftop party before it gets started. Can you help them pick out some awesome clothes and accessories before their super cool night begins in this dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Pre-Concert Rooftop Party

documents.description: These princesses are all going to the Oscars this year! They’ve never been before, and they definitely want to look their best before it’s time for them to head to Hollywood. Can you help them quickly choose their hairstyles, gowns, and more in this fabulous dress-up game?
documents.title: Princesses: Oscars Design

documents.description: Will you find yourself stuck behind the 8 ball in this multiplayer version of pool, the classic billiards game? Compete against other gamers from all across the globe while you try to get all of your balls into the pockets.
documents.title: 8 Ball Online

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep fighting in this epic multiplayer action game? Join gamers from all across the world for a civil war involving several of the world’s greatest superheroes! You can transform into cooler and more powerful characters while you collect power pellets and attack your opponents.
documents.title: Superhero.io

documents.description: Oh no! This poor mommy was in a bad accident, and she’s just arrived in the ER! Can you help treat her injuries in this online medical simulation game? You’ll need to check her heart rate, bandage her wounds, and more. With your help, both her and her baby should be okay.
documents.title: Beauty Mommy: Accident ER

documents.description: Are you ready to join the jungle princess on her latest adventure? There’s a huge amount of jewels that she’s trying to link together in this awesome match 3 puzzle game. Go on a journey through her kingdom while she smashes through the jewels’ seals and uses lots of powerful boosters.
documents.title: Jewels Blitz 4

documents.description: It’s time for this former mermaid to go searching for a whole new style! Can you help her decide what to do with her hair in this online makeover simulation game? Join her while she creates a magical look and designs an awesome outfit, too.
documents.title: Magical Mermaid Hairstyle

documents.description: Things are about to get wild in this downright explosive multiplayer action game. Take on gamers from all over the planet while you try to blast them to bits. You’ll need to dodge their mortar shells while you launch your own directly at their heads!
documents.title: Mortar.io

documents.description: Ander is about to become a student at Ogdoad’s Magic School, an exclusive academy for witches and wizards. Unfortunately, the grounds are filled with dangerous monsters called Magimons. Join him while he teams up with a talking wand and some other magical tools in this turn-based adventure game. Can you help make sure that Ander’s first week at the academy isn’t a complete disaster?
documents.title: Magikmon

documents.description: Will you be able to get a high-score and earn some awesome achievements in this exciting puzzle game? Try to find room for each of these unusually-shaped pieces on the board. Can you squeeze them all in?
documents.title: 2020 Plus

documents.description: There’s a rumor going around campus that one of these princesses is the most fashionable girl at the university. Can you help determine which one is the best dressed in this online dress-up and design game? You’ll need to choose some awesome outfits, makeup, and accessories for each one of them.
documents.title: Princess: Campus Gossip

documents.description: This coloring book is filled with unicorns that are incredibly adorable. How will you decorate them in this online coloring game? You can give them pink hair and cover them in all sorts of other wonderful and wild colors.
documents.title: Coloring Book: Fabulous Cute Unicorn

documents.description: Here’s somebody you can really kick around! This dummy will still be your buddy after you pummel him with everything from grenades to your own two feet in this weird and wacky action game. Every time you hit him, you’ll earn coins for upgrades and better weapons like pistols and machine guns!
documents.title: Super Buddy Kick

documents.description: The crafty thief in this hidden objects game is trying to become the best one in town. Can you help her show off her skills while she plans a series of daring robberies? She’ll need to build up her reputation points while she searches for specific and very valuable things to steal in a variety of houses, museums, and more!
documents.title: Hidden Objects: Super Thief

documents.description: Those romantic balls are at it once again! Can you help them get together in this physics-based action game? They’re really in the mood to do some smooching!
documents.title: Love Balls 2

documents.description: This girl is using her magical powers to create lots of fantastic and exotic pets. Find out what happens when she mixes together a variety of really random ingredients like strawberries, rubber ducks, and chocolate chip cookies with an enchanted egg. There’s 12 different pets that she can create in this online game.
documents.title: Fantasy Pet: Spell Factory

documents.description: Eve has gone missing! Now it’s up to Adam to rescue her in this wild point and click adventure game. Can you help the crafty caveman while he goes in search of her? He’s about to begin a very exciting journey!
documents.title: Adam and Eve 6

documents.description: Get ready to meet some really marvelous monsters! Don’t worry, they’re very friendly. Can you put them all back together again in this cute online puzzle game? You’ll need to reassemble their various parts. There’s also three different modes that will really challenge your jigsaw puzzle skills.
documents.title: Jigsaw Puzzle: Funny Monsters

documents.description: There’s several different adventures that you can go on in this realistic 3D driving game. Find out if you can be the first one to cross the finish line in a thrilling street race or challenge your opponents in a dangerous competition. There’s also lots of awesome upgrades and classic cars you can try out.
documents.title: Real Street Racing

documents.description: Lady Bug is a famous superhero who fights crime and villains on the streets of Paris. That doesn’t leave her much time for fashion! Can you help her and her friends create some awesome new styles in this dress-up and design game? They could really use some outfits that are as cool and exciting as they are!
documents.title: Lady Bug and Friends Maker

documents.description: Summer selfies are a great thing to post on your favorite social media app. These three princesses are about to create some in this online design and simulation game. Can you help them put together the perfect summer styles before it’s time for their photos to be taken? They’ll need to choose the right outfits, makeup, and locations as well.
documents.title: Princesses: Summer Selfie

documents.description: If you thought transporting normal cargo was tough, just wait until you attempt to drive with these hungry dinosaurs in the back of your rig! There’s three different and intense modes in this 3D driving game that will let you put your skills to the ultimate test. Can you get this Tyrannosaurus Rex and his prehistoric friends to the zoo before time runs out?
documents.title: Dino Transport

documents.description: This former mermaid is still adjusting to her new life on land. She just got a job as a barista in a coffee shop. Can you help her keep up with all of her customers’ orders in this business simulation game? She’ll need to make everything from Caffe Americanos to lattes while she chooses which designs to put in the foam. She can create awesome art featuring leaves, cats, bears, and more!
documents.title: Mermaid Barista: Latte Art

documents.description: This fashionable girl and her friends are creating some new styles based on their favorite emojis. What types of clothing, hairstyles, and shoes fit their moods, though? Help them try to create the perfect matches in this online dress-up and design game.
documents.title: Emoji Mood Makeover

documents.description: Which one of these three stylish princesses will win this year’s beauty pageant in their kingdom? That all depends on your fashion skills in this fabulous dress-up game! Help them choose the right hairstyles, outfits, and accessories before it’s time for them to hit the stage.
documents.title: Princess Beauty Pageant

documents.description: Have you ever wanted to drive a train? Now you can in this awesome 3D driving simulation game. Take a seat in the locomotive and see if you can handle the pressure of a trip down the rails. You’ll have to carefully consider your speed while you change tracks, avoid colliding with other trains, and much more. Will you be able to get your train to the next station in one piece?
documents.title: Train Driver Simulator

documents.description: How long will you be able to play this gooey puzzle game? You’ll need to keep placing these gummy blocks on the board until you run out of space. Fortunately, there’s bombs you can collect along the way that will help you clear out a few areas while you play.
documents.title: Gummy Blocks: Evolution

documents.description: Five different and super awesome monster trucks are waiting for you to take them for a spin in this 3D racing game. Jump behind the wheel before you zoom through a desert and later a forest filled with ramps, hills, and some other really wild and totally xtreme hazards. There’s dozens of tracks in both areas that will really test your virtual driving skills.
documents.title: Xtreme Monster Truck

documents.description: It’s almost time for this stylish girl to celebrate her birthday in this dress-up game. Can you choose some awesome outfits for her and her friends? They’re planning to spend the afternoon eating tons of super yummy ice cream. You can even decide which flavors they should try first.
documents.title: Ice Cream Birthday Party

documents.description: This master chef has decided to take on a new challenge. He wants to find out if he can manage a successful food cart. Can you help him meet his daily goals and earn enough cash in this time management and business simulation game? He’ll need to make meals for his hungry customers as fast as he can!
documents.title: Street Food: Master Chef

documents.description: You’ve probably played a soccer game before but what about a soccar game? Take control of these rocket-powered and robotic vehicles as they hit the field and attempt to score tons of goals. Will you be able to lead your team to victory while you compete against other gamers from around the world in this exciting multiplayer sports game?
documents.title: Rocket Soccar

documents.description: Will you be able to master this 3D puzzle game? You’ll need to slide the tiles into the correct locations. The goal is to make both them and the lines connecting them all the same color. Find out if you can beat each and every last one of the game’s very tricky levels.
documents.title: OXXO

documents.description: You can use sniper rifles and even bazookas to eliminate your opponents in this multiplayer shooter game. Dive into the battle and challenge players from all around the globe. Will you survive long enough to see the clock run down to zero in each thrilling death-match?
documents.title: Sniper Clash 3D

documents.description: K-pop is one of the coolest types of pop music out there! That’s why all of these four princesses just can’t get enough of their favorite groups. One of them just arrived in their kingdom from Korea to begin a tour, and they’ve got tickets to their first concert. Can you help the princesses choose some awesome outfits for what’s sure to be an unforgettable night in this online dress-up game?
documents.title: Princesses: K-Pop Fans

documents.description: How fast will you be able to connect all of this juicy fruit and candy in this vibrant match 3 puzzle game? There’s lots of raspberries, gummies, and more that are waiting for you to link them together. You can also use awesome power-ups along the way that will help you remove them all from the playing board.
documents.title: Tasty Jewels

documents.description: How long will your snake become in this 3D multiplayer online game? You’ll need to eat tons of glowing pellets to make it the most powerful reptile around. If you’d rather not play as a snake, you can also take control of a subway train, a line of athletes, and more!
documents.title: Blocky Snakes io

documents.description: Eliza is about to open a new pet shop, but there’s still tons of work she needs to get done. Can you help her quickly prepare for her opening day in this magical business simulation game? She’ll need to stick to her budget while she gathers all the supplies and super cute animals she’ll need for her shop.
documents.title: Eliza's Pet Shop

documents.description: You’ll need perfect timing to earn a high score while you play this intense action game. Take control of the spinning dots and see if you can get them to merge with the ones flying right toward them!
documents.title: Catch Dots

documents.description: Will you be able to piece together all of these gorgeous jigsaw puzzles? They feature everything from classic European destinations to cats snoozing in the sun. There’s also different difficulty settings that are perfect for new players and experts alike!
documents.title: Epic Jigsaw Puzzle

documents.description: Summer is here and these fashionable girls are breaking out all the latest styles. You can join them while they choose the perfect outfits for a bike ride, hanging out in their backyard, and a fun barbecue.
documents.title: Girly Summer Patterns

documents.description: The classic game returns in this retro online version. Enjoy 8-bit graphics while you try to make your snake as powerful as possible. You can change the snake's speed settings before you help it gobble up as many tasty apples as possible.
documents.title: Classic Snake

documents.description: Oh no! This very sleepy princess is in the middle of a serious emergency! Can you help this paramedic quickly treat her condition before it’s too late in this medical simulation game?
documents.title: Sleepy Princess: Resurrection

documents.description: It’s almost time for these princesses to go searching for their favorite brands in a few of the shops in this awesome mall. Can you help them track down tons of cool outfits, makeup, and accessories in this online shopping and dress-up game?
documents.title: Princesses: Favorite Brands Shopping

documents.description: It’s almost time for these girls to load up their awesome party van and head to Coachella, one of the coolest outdoor music festivals of the year. What should they wear, though? Oh, and how should they do their hair? You can help them decide in this online dress-up and design game.
documents.title: Coachella Party Van

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep playing this intense mathematical puzzle game? You’ll need to prevent the numbered cubes from reaching the bottom of the screen. Hurl cubes with the same numbers at them until they add up to 2,048. It’s much tougher than it might seem, but there’s lots of helpful power-ups that will help you stay in the game.
documents.title: 2048 Lines

documents.description: Are you ready for battle? Head back to the world of Kogama in this online game and fight your opponents with every weapon that you can get your hands on.
documents.title: KOGAMA: War 4

documents.description: Will you be able to get the marble past the finish line in this intense 3D racing game? It’s about to zoom down a twisted and turbulent obstacle course that features steep drops, super sharp spikes, and absolutely no safety standards whatsoever!
documents.title: Twisty Road

documents.description: The kingdom has been almost completely invaded by your enemy’s armies. Now it’s time to strike back in this real-time strategy game. Defend your last remaining territory by building futuristic defensive towers before you set out to liberate the rest of the kingdom. During your journey, you can also buy awesome magical upgrades that will make your knights and their weapons even more powerful.
documents.title: Kingdom Tower Defense

documents.description: This fashionable princess and her friends have just arrived in Tokyo, Japan. They’re eager to check out the hottest styles in Harajuku, the city’s famous fashion district. You can join them while they go shopping for lots of awesome outfits in this online dress-up game.
documents.title: Harajuku Japan Fashion

documents.description: Needless to say, this party is going to get pretty crazy and incredibly dangerous, too! How long will you survive once you join other gamers from all over the planet in this first-person shooter game? Dive into a series of fights to the finish with them. There’s certain goals like death counts that you can try to achieve during each action-packed battle.
documents.title: Bullet Party

documents.description: These four celebrities have been thinking about Malibu a lot lately. They miss its beaches and cool cafes. Most of all, they miss the famous city’s awesome boutiques. Can you help them recreate the trendy outfits they’d find in them in this dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Celebs: Malibu Fashion Trends

documents.description: Try to beat the objectives in each challenging level that’s waiting for you in this match 3 puzzle game. You can earn lots of points while you try to connect the numbers on these various pairs of hexagons. Switch them around to find space for them on the board while you play.
documents.title: Hexagon

documents.description: Will you be able to survive for hours or only a few seconds in this multiplayer action game? Join warriors from around the world in an epic fight to the finish. You can collect power pellets to boost your abilities while you struggle to stay alive.
documents.title: Weapon.io

documents.description: Within this mysterious temple, there’s an exciting puzzle adventure that awaits you! How long will you be able to mix and merge all of the magical shapes? There’s two different ways that you can remove them from the board in this exciting puzzle game. Create some awesome strategies while you attempt to make them all explode!
documents.title: Element Blocks

documents.description: These girls are really craving some cupcakes! Fortunately, they have a new app that will let them order some from an awesome local bakery. Can you help them decide which ones to get in this cute online simulation game? You can choose the toppings, the types of frosting, and more!
documents.title: InstaYum: Handmade Sweets

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep the ball rolling in this exciting 3D action game? Roll it down a series of slopes while it dodges barriers and makes breathtaking leaps.
documents.title: Crazy Roll 3D

documents.description: It’s time for these fashionable girls to go on a shopping spree. Join them while they search for some awesome and new styles in all of their favorite stores and boutiques. You can help them pick out all sorts of great clothes, accessories, and more!
documents.title: Girls Fun Shopping

documents.description: This adorable cat loves cleaning almost as much as he loves riding around on his owner’s robotic vacuum. You can tag along with him while he cleans every inch of their house in this online puzzle game. Can you make sure the cat doesn’t miss even a single spot while he zooms through every room?  He'll start partying after you complete each challenging level.
documents.title: Party Cat

documents.description: It’s time for this princess to use her fashion and doodling skills to freshen up not just her own style, but her city’s style as well. Join her while she creates new outfits and chooses some fantastic makeup in this online dress-up and design game. Once she’s done, she’s going to decorate a few streets downtown.
documents.title: Princess: Downtown Doodle Fashion

documents.description: Have you ever wondered what it’s like to be a wedding planner? You can learn more about this awesome career in this online simulation game. You’ll be in charge of organizing an awesome beach wedding. You’ll need to look over the bride’s list of everything she wants at the ceremony. Will you be able to design her bouquet, gown, and more?
documents.title: Beach Wedding Planner

documents.description: One or two players can enjoy this retro sports game. You can customize your character before you participate in a variety of different competitions in an awesome global tournament. Join one of a variety of international teams before you show off your skills in the weightlifting competition, go for the gold in the 100 meter sprinting race, and more!
documents.title: Sports Hero

documents.description: If you survive this epic series of battles to the death, you might just become a lord! Grab your bow and arrow before you try to eliminate the competition in this medieval and multiplayer action game.
documents.title: Bowroyale.io

documents.description: These princesses are about to break all the rules of fashion in this outrageous dress-up and design game. You can join them while they work on a few new outfits that are brave, bold, and totally outrageous. In their opinion, fashion shouldn’t even have rules!
documents.title: Princesses: No Rules Fashion

documents.description: Your enemies are headed toward the gates! You’ll need to quickly learn how to shoot your new bow before they arrive to raid the castle in this 3D action game. Practice your shooting skills before it’s time to start defending it. You can collect coins with each enemy you kill that you can later use to buy cool upgrades for your character.
documents.title: Archer Master 3D: Castle Defense

documents.description: Will you be able to keep up with all of the colorful blocks in this match 3 puzzle game? If they reach the top of the screen, it’ll be game over! Connect them as fast as you can to remove them from the board.
documents.title: Panelore

documents.description: These shapes are falling fast! Will you be able to fit them into all of the holes before it’s too late? They’re shaped like cats, butterflies, and even snowflakes. Try to get them to slide through the holes in this fast-paced 3D action game.
documents.title: Falling Shape

documents.description: This girl’s best friend wants her to tag along on a trip to the new retro arcade in their town. She isn’t so sure and should probably stay home tonight and study. Maybe a cool outfit would change her mind? Quickly create some styles that are straight out of the ‘80s for both of them in this nostalgic dress-up game.
documents.title: Retro Arcade Days

documents.description: It’s time for these four girls to get in shape! Choose some awesome workout clothes for them before they hit the gym. They may even try out some cool sports, too!
documents.title: BFF's Fitness Lifestyle

documents.description: You can help not just one but fourteen different princesses in this online dress-up game. They’re all about to attend an awesome outdoor music festival. Can you give them your favorite fashion tips while they choose what makeup to put on and what outfits they should wear?
documents.title: Princess Music Festival

documents.description: This adorable kitty has tons of candy to link together in this enchanted kingdom. Can you help him out during what’s sure to be an awesome adventure in this match 3 puzzle game? You’ll need to connect all of these explosives sweets. If you can match up five or more, they’ll blow up!
documents.title: Candy Match

documents.description: Nobody ever said that driving a garbage truck was easy. First, there’s the smell you have to deal with along with having to lift all those trash cans. Fortunately, you won’t have to put up with any of that in this 3D driving game. Just drive the garbage truck to the correct locations in each exciting level before the clock runs down to zero.
documents.title: Garbage Truck Simulator

documents.description: It’s a total feeding frenzy in this wild io game! Take control of a wacky worm before you challenge other players from all across the globe. Will you be able to make your worm huge and powerful while it gobbles up lots of ladybugs, cherries, and other crazy stuff?
documents.title: Wormax2.io

documents.description: All of these poor plants are incredibly thirsty! They’re depending on you to give them water in this cute puzzle game since their watering can keeps falling asleep. You’ll need to create a path for his water to flow over to them. Connect the tiles on the playing board as quickly as you can before they dry up!
documents.title: Water Me Please

documents.description: Will you survive each one of these intense duels to the death? Take control of your archer in this exciting action game. You’ll need to hit all of your opponents with your arrows before they eliminate you with their own weapons!
documents.title: Stickman Archer: Mr. Bow

documents.description: There’s a flurry of orders that Noelle is dealing with in this exciting time management and business simulation game. It’s incredibly busy at her popular cafe. Can you help her out while she handles the customers at each table? You’ll need to quickly make some hot dogs, burgers, and more.
documents.title: Noelle's Food Flurry

documents.description: Will you be able to sink all of your shots in this online version of the popular billiards game? See if you can knock the balls into the correct pockets in each challenging level. Grab a pool cue and get ready to prove that you’re a star when it comes to this classic game.
documents.title: 8 Ball Pool Stars

documents.description: These three young princesses just arrived at their summer camp in this dress-up and design game. Can you help them pick out some cool clothes before they design their tents and fill them with lots of awesome pillows and decorations?
documents.title: Princesses at the Summer Camp

documents.description: Eliza decided to go on a cruise this summer. She just stepped off the ship and onto a gorgeous tropical island. Help her relax with a delicious smoothie before she tries out some new makeup and more.
documents.title: Eliza's Summer Cruise

documents.description: Will you be able to keep these cute glasses happy in this challenging puzzle game? There’s three different modes that could keep you playing for hours. Try to fill the glasses to the exact water line or flip them into the correct spots. You’ll need some quick reflexes and a sharp eye to beat every level!
documents.title: Happy Glass 2

documents.description: These fashionable girls are sharing their latest stories and styles on their favorite app. Join them while they create a few awesome looks with lots of new makeup, clothes, and more!
documents.title: Online Selfie Stories

documents.description: The streets are about to be filled with the sound of gunfire in this 3D action game. How long will you manage to stay alive? Go up against other players from around the world while you defend your turf. You’ll be joining a group of gangsters before you attempt to wipe out your competition with Tommy guns, vintage automobiles, and more.
documents.title: Downtown 1930s Mafia

documents.description: All of these animals have been looking for a new place to live in this adorable action game. Can you help them dodge traffic while they try to make it to the farm that will serve as their new home? These highways are dangerous!
documents.title: Animal Rescue

documents.description: These royal couples just arrived at an exclusive beach resort where they’ll be spending their honeymoons. Can you help them each choose some awesome outfits before they explore the resort in this dress-up game?
documents.title: Royal Honeymoon Vacation

documents.description: These motorcycles were built for speed! Get ready to take them on an awesome series of road trips in this 3D driving game. You can dodge other vehicles while you race through a desert, a forest, and more. You can even buy cooler bikes and upgrades along the way.
documents.title: Highway Bike Racers

documents.description: Some of these emojis are happy, others are sad, and a few of them look like they’re going to puke at any second! Can you match them all up in this hilarious bubble shooter game? Put them into groups of three or more to make them explode!
documents.title: Emoji Bubble

documents.description: Why settle for a boring purse when you can have a totally wild one instead? These princesses are searching for some truly crazy ones in this online game! Join them during their next shopping spree while they search for purses that are shaped like cats, ladybugs, and even doughnuts. You can also help them choose their outfits.
documents.title: Princesses: Kooky Purses

documents.description: How many of these chickens can you get across this busy highway? They’re determined to make it to the other side, even though it’s incredibly dangerous. They’ll need to avoid all the speeding vehicles before they try to get across the river. Will you be able to keep all of these crazy cluckers safe in this adorable online action game?
documents.title: Go Chicken Go

documents.description: It’s time for these princesses to check out the coolest trends of the season! Tag along with them while they go in search of the latest styles in this dress-up game. They’ll be trying out lots of new outfits that feature animal prints, bright colors, and so much more!
documents.title: Princesses: Summer Trends

documents.description: How far will you fly in this wild and crazy sports game? Send your shopping cart and its rider blasting down a hill before you find out how much distance it can cover. He’ll be able to collect coins if he lands safely on the other side. You’ll also be able to buy awesome upgrades and cool stunts between levels.
documents.title: Shopping Cart HD

documents.description: Yuki just can’t decide what to do this morning. That’s why she’s going to use a roulette wheel that features lots of different activities. Join her while she spins the wheel and finds out if she’ll be designing a cool outfit, making a yummy meal, or something else!
documents.title: Yuki's Fun Roulette

documents.description:
Ahoy, matey! Ye have been marooned on a tropical island with other pirates...
Only one will survive and plunder the booty. Give no quarter!
documents.title: Yohoho.io

documents.description: It’s almost time for this fabulous fashionista to explore a tropical resort in the Maldives. She just arrived and wants to look her best. Can you quickly choose a hairstyle for her along with an awesome outfit? She could really use your advice in this online dress-up game.
documents.title: Fashionista Maldives: Real Makeover

documents.description: You can play everything from classic symphonies by Beethoven to children’s songs in this music game. Can you keep the beat while you try to hit all the keys at just the right moments?
documents.title: Piano Online

documents.description: The city is under attack! Will you be able to defend it before it’s too late? You can use everything from handguns to sniper rifles to take down your targets in this 3D shooter game.
documents.title: Rebel Attack Shooter

documents.description: These two skaters are the best of friends! They’ll be looking for some awesome new outfits this afternoon before they start designing two skateboards. Can you help them choose a few totally cool styles in this dress-up and design game?
documents.title: Skater Friends

documents.description: There’s lots of adorable pictures of cartoon airplanes and their pilots that you can put back together again in this online jigsaw puzzle game. You can try out three different modes as well. Play with the easy one before you move on to the medium or hard one!
documents.title: Jigsaw Puzzle: Cartoon Airplanes

documents.description: Will this ball make it all the way to the bottom of the towers in this online action game? That all depends on your skills and reflexes. You’ll have to move fast to prevent it from getting destroyed by one of the barriers.
documents.title: Stack Fall 3D

documents.description: These four stylish princesses are eager to get out and about with their babies. Can you help them choose some awesome outfits before they leave? They’ll be using some baby carriers instead of strollers.
documents.title: Princesses: Baby Wearing Fun

documents.description: This fashionable girl has always wondered what it’s like to be a celebrity. Join her while she learns more about their way of life in this dress-up game. Can you help her look like a world famous singer or actress after she designs some really cool outfits?
documents.title: The Celebrity Way of Life

documents.description: You can play with 25, 49, or even 100 pieces in this cute jigsaw puzzle game. See how fast you can put together the lions, elephants, hippopotamuses, and more!
documents.title: Wild Animals Jigsaw Puzzle

documents.description: Put on your cowboy hat and start creating and playing your own amazing Wild West game!
documents.title: KOGAMA: West Town

documents.description: Zombies have completely taken over this top secret laboratory! Now it’s up to you and a friend to put an end to the madness in this cooperative action game. Can you wipe out the undead while you attempt to escape?
documents.title: Zombie Mission: 2 Player

documents.description: Abby is enjoying a fun afternoon with her latest crafting projects. Can you help her while she works on some new designs for a few of her outfits, her backpack, and more?
documents.title: Baby Abby: Funny Crafting Day

documents.description: This fashionista just arrived at an exclusive seaside resort. Can you help her relax in its luxurious spa in this onilne simulation game? She wants to enjoy the jacuzzi, get a pedicure, and more.
documents.title: Beach Spa Salon

documents.description: Just look at all the cool and crazy emojis that you can put back together in this online puzzle game. Piece together happy faces, laughing faces, and other faces that are totally wild! There’s three different and challenging modes that will really test your jigsaw puzzle skills.
documents.title: Emoji Jigsaw Puzzle Challenge

documents.description: There’s several totally awesome off-road vehicles that you can try out in this 3D driving game. Explore the city in a pickup truck, an ATV, or even a super cool military jeep!
documents.title: 4 x 4 Off-Roader

documents.description: How will you decorate all of these super cute gators? Use your imagination while you create some totally wild new looks for them in this online coloring game. There’s four different drawings that you can color.
documents.title: Alligator Coloring Book

documents.description: Welcome to Titania’s kingdom, an enchanted land filled with all sorts of mysterious and magical creatures. Even in a place as unusual and exciting as this one, Titania wants to look her best. Can you help her create a new style that’s truly magical with some awesome makeup and dresses in this makeover game?
documents.title: Titania: Queen of the Fairies

documents.description: This shark is completely fed up with all of the humans who keep swimming in his favorite bay. Now it’s time for him to strike back in this weird and wild action game. Tag along with him while he gobbles up scuba divers, destroys boats, and even yanks police helicopters out of the sky!
documents.title: Angry Shark Online

documents.description: There will be a new crossword puzzle waiting for you every day that you play this challenging online game. Will you be able to fill in the blanks while you attempt to correctly answer all the questions?
documents.title: Crossword Daily

documents.description: Uh-oh! Tom just got caught trying to pick sunflowers in a farmer’s field. Now the farmer is determined to capture him in this 3D action game. Can you help him get away from the farmer while he races through this chaotic town? Tom can use skateboards and even an awesome jet to get away from the fearsome farmer!
documents.title: Tom Run

documents.description: The summer has finally begun, and the time is right for a party. All these fashionable girls need to do is decide what to wear. Help them pick out some cool clothes for what’s sure to be an amazing day in this dress-up and design game.
documents.title: Summertime Celebration

documents.description: Explore a kingdom that’s high in the sky with this installment of the popular world-building game. Jump across huge gaps and find out what’s beyond every corner while you roam alongside players from all around the planet.
documents.title: KOGAMA: Sky Land

documents.description: How fast can you put together all of these awesome pictures of animals in this online puzzle game? You can assemble cows, goats, and other barnyard critters.
documents.title: Farm Animals Jigsaw Puzzle

documents.description: These clumsy creatures are about to tour the entire world. Unfortunately, there’s a good chance they’ll be dead before they make it far. Can you help them avoid getting hurt in this wacky and wild action game? You’ll need to help them fly airplanes, stay safe while surfing on the sand around the Egyptian pyramids, and much more!
documents.title: Dumb Ways To Die 3: World Tour

documents.description: There’s always something delicious on the menu at Annie’s shop, but what should she make today? Will it be cakes, pies, or lots of super yummy muffins? Help her decide in this cooking and business simulation game before her first customer arrives!
documents.title: Annie's Handmade Sweets Shop

documents.description: You can create your very own rock star with Loli and all of her friends in this dress-up and design game. You can choose the color of their hair, their outfit, and lots more!
documents.title: Loli Rock Star Maker

documents.description: What’s the secret behind Rosie’s amazing fashion skills? She likes to wear tons of different types of outfits. You can help her create one for each day of the week in this online dress-up and design game.
documents.title: Rosie's Fashion Week

documents.description: An epic series of adventures and competitions are waiting for you on the tropical islands in this racing game. Jump into one of these wacky vehicles and head to the starting line. Your next race is about to begin!
documents.title: Uphill Adventure Drivers

documents.description: There’s tons of challenging levels and missions that are waiting for you in this realistic 3D driving simulation game. Will you be able to safely transport your cargo while you make your way through the countrysides of India? Jump behind the wheel of each one of these big rigs while you attempt to make it to each unloading area before time runs out.
documents.title: Indian Truck Simulator 3D

documents.description: You can explore an entire universe of puzzles in this online game. Try out each and every one of the jigsaw puzzles that feature various different planets. You can also change the difficulty settings if you’re searching for a real challenge.
documents.title: Planet Jigsaw Challenge

documents.description: You can piece together nine awesome drawings of dinosaurs in this online jigsaw puzzle game. Will you be able to assemble the Tyrannosaurus rex and all of his dino friends? You can change the settings in order to use as few as 16 pieces or as many as 100!
documents.title: Dino Jigsaw Puzzle

documents.description: Something really weird has been happening with the Dotted Girl’s tongue lately. The famous superhero might have some sort of an infection! Can you give her a quick exam at her doctor’s office in this medical simulation game?
documents.title: Dotted Girl: Tongue Doctor

documents.description: You’ve probably never played an online coloring game quite like this one before! Can you decorate all of these three-dimensional images? You can color everything from dogs and cats to bicycles and helicopters!
documents.title: Pixel Art 3D

documents.description: So many germs, so little time! Jump into this microscopic spaceship and wage war on some truly violent viruses! Will you be able to destroy all of them while you collect coins that you can use to buy awesome weapons and upgrades?
documents.title: Germ War

documents.description: These two designers have challenged each other to come up with the best outfits that all celebrate their favorite types of animals. Can you help them create some really wild styles in this online dress-up and design game? They really want to impress their followers on their favorite social media app!
documents.title: Animal Trends: Social Media Adventure

documents.description: Will you be able to correctly identify the animals in all of these photos? They’ll start out easy, but they’ll get more difficult with each passing level in this word puzzle and trivia game.
documents.title: Animal Photo Quiz

documents.description: How many of these free kicks will you be able to make in this 3D sports game? Head to the blacktop where a crowd has already gathered to cheer you on. They’re all huge soccer fans, and they’re hoping you can get the ball into the goal each time.
documents.title: Street Free Kick 3D

documents.description: How many of these colorful dots will you be able to send into the spinning circle? You’ll need perfect timing to hit the right spot and get them into the circle in the center. Prove you’ve got amazing reflexes with this intense action game.
documents.title: Color Circles

documents.description: You’ll have a blast while you battle your way across a kingdom filled with fun and adventure. Can you prevent the marbles from reaching the portal in each one of the action-packed levels that are waiting for you in this match 3 puzzle game?
documents.title: Marble Blast

documents.description: Which side will dominate in this real-time strategy game? Maybe more importantly, how many tanks will wind up in the scrapheap? Carefully deploy each one of your war machines as you attempt to destroy your enemy’s base.
documents.title: Clash of Tanks

documents.description: Have you got what it takes to become a hero for both your team and your fans in this sports game? Grab a bat and find out if you can really wow the crowd at this cricket grounds.
documents.title: Cricket Hero

documents.description: Doughnuts covered in colorful sprinkles are one of these princesses’ favorite treats! That’s why they’re designing some super cute styles inspired by them. Can you help these fashionable royals create a few outfits that are totally sweet and stylish?
documents.title: Princesses: Sprinkle Doughnuts

documents.description: Ellie is living a life full of luxury and fashion in this dress-up and design game. You can tag along with her while she creates lots of cool outfits and works on improving her daily routine.
documents.title: Ellie: Life in Luxury

documents.description: This ball is really on a roll in this 3D action game. How long will you be able to keep it moving? Help it blast down these platforms while it collects lots of diamonds. Accuracy is really important, so you’ll have to be careful!
documents.title: Ball Surfer 3D

documents.description: These adorable babies are all the same...or are they? Find out if you can spot all of the differences in this cute and challenging puzzle game.
documents.title: Find the Differences: Sweet Babies

documents.description: Can you keep each one of these enchanted totems safe in this physics-based action game? They’re all standing on a stone platform. Carefully remove the wooden blocks beneath the totems while you attempt to prevent them from tumbling to the ground.
documents.title: Totem Destroyer Redux

documents.description: Pastels are really in right now! Join these three girls while they create some totally awesome styles in this online dress-up game. They’re going to experiment with cool makeup, outfits, and more!
documents.title: Pastel Crush Girls

documents.description: You’ll definitely have a ball while you play this physics-based action game. These two magical balls are in love with one another. Use your drawing skills to create lines and ramps that will help them reach one another.
documents.title: Love Balls

documents.description: These numbered hexagons are slowly headed toward your cannon. If they get there, it’s going to be destroyed! How quickly will you be able to fend them off in this physics-based action game? You’ll need to carefully choose when to fire the cannon in order to destroy as many of them as possible.
documents.title: Hex Blaster

documents.description: Jaclyn knows pretty much everything there is to know about fashion. You can join her while she designs a batch of awesome styles for an entire month in this dress-up game. Team up with her to create lots of cool outfits and more!
documents.title: Jaclyn: Best Style Month

documents.description: It’s time to get ready for a royal rumble! Your kingdom was invaded while you were away on a dangerous quest. Can you take it back, one building at a time, in this epic puzzle game? Match up the tiles while you reclaim everything from your citizens’ humble cabins to your own former castle!
documents.title: Medieval Battle

documents.description: These royals are getting ready for the trip of a lifetime. They’re going on an epic hiking trek in this dress-up game. Can you help them choose some awesome outfits that will be both fashionable and strong enough to handle the trails they’ll be on?
documents.title: Princess: Hiking in Style

documents.description: She’s old, she’s bold, and she’s ready for revenge! Team up with this grumpy granny while she attacks everything and everyone from carelessly discarded couches to annoying teenagers in this wild and crazy action game. Just make sure that she doesn’t accidentally hit a police officer with her giant hammer!
documents.title: Angry Gran

documents.description: Do blondes really do it better when it comes to fashion and partying? It’s time to find out in this wild online dress-up game. You can help these three blondes put together some cool outfits for an evening at their favorite club.
documents.title: Blondes do it Better

documents.description: Have you got what it takes to survive as an outlaw on the streets of Ancient Rome? Swing your sword and search for even better weapons while you take on its bravest warriors in this 3D action and adventure game.
documents.title: Rome Legionnaire Simulator

documents.description: What answers will you receive from the mysterious and mystical board? It’s time to find out in this strange online game. Ask it any question that you like and see what happens next!
documents.title: Ouija Voices

documents.description: The kitchen in this busy cafe is totally crazy! Will you be able to keep up with all of the customers’ orders in this action-packed, business simulation game? The ingredients are getting flung all over the place. You’ll have to grab them while they fly across the screen as you prepare each dish.
documents.title: Chopstick Cooking

documents.description: This snake might be little, but he’s about to begin an awfully big adventure! Unfortunately, he gets tuckered out pretty easily. Can you help him keep his energy level up while he continues his exciting journey in this adorable action game?
documents.title: Wiggle

documents.description: This girl really loves unicorns and has been thinking about getting a new hairstyle. She’s looking for one that’s anything but conventional! Can you help her while she comes up with a look that’s totally magical in this makeover game?
documents.title: Unicorn Hairstyles

documents.description: How long will you be able to keep combining the jellies in this challenging puzzle game? Slide and smoosh them together while you try to play for as long as possible.
documents.title: Jelly Pop 2048

documents.description: This baby pixie has had a very busy day! Now it’s time to get her all cleaned up in this enchanting online game. Can you give her a quick bath in her magical tub?
documents.title: Pixie Baby Bath

documents.description: You can take a trip through time to an alternate reality where steam powers an entire kingdom in this dress-up game. Each one of its princesses is getting ready for another day filled with fantasy and adventure. Can you help them all quickly put together some totally awesome steampunk outfits?
